   241	
   242	Orion/NetSuite CRM requires opportunity entry with validated minimum fields, creating mandatory discipline for pipeline visibility. The Kanban board visualization (Opportunity Cards in Orion white paper) provides intuitive drag-and-drop interface for pipeline management, replacing spreadsheet tracking. Visibility restriction ensures sales reps see only their opportunities, maintaining focus without the distraction of company-wide activity feed.
   243	
   244	Validation rules prevent progression without required information. Custom fields capture all necessary context (territory, source, sector, expected close date, etc.). The system can flag opportunities missing required fields, preventing advancement until data is complete.
