Financial Management/KBMH/3 Output/BRD_FinancialManagement_v2.0.md:880:- Two distinct GP metrics for different audiences: true project profitability vs. commission-eligible earnings
Financial Management/KBMH/3 Output/BRD_FinancialManagement_v2.0.md:881:- Evidence: "That's why we have two... different set of KPIs... So, we have a set of KPIs for project gross profit, and then we have commissionable gross profit" - Kipp
