    29	KBM Hoag's marketing organization operates fundamentally differently from traditional B2B marketing functions. Rather than building demand generation infrastructure, the marketing team serves as relationship coordinators and RFP response specialists—directly supporting sales through targeted communications to key influencers (brokers, architects, project managers, general contractors) and coordinating complex proposal processes.
