    69	# SECTION 1: PURCHASE REQUISITIONS & PROCUREMENT CONTROL
    70	
    71	## 1.1 Your Business Requirements
    72	
    73	**REQ-001: Implement purchase requisition approval workflow (ALIGNS)**
    74	
    75	KBM Hogue needs to enforce controlled purchasing through purchase requisitions that require supervisor approval before items can be ordered. The team made an explicit decision to use purchase requisitions, indicating a commitment to improving purchasing governance and creating audit trails for compliance and budget control purposes.
    76	
    77	**Requirements Classification:**
    78	- Type: Functional - Purchasing control process
    79	- Priority: Must-Have
    80	- Users Impacted: Employees requesting purchases, supervisors approving requests, procurement team, finance
    81	
    82	---
    83	
    84	## 1.2 Current State Process
    85	
    86	**PROCESS:** Purchase Request & Approval (Current State)
    87	
    88	**TRIGGER:** Employee needs to purchase materials or services
    89	
    90	**CURRENT STEPS:**
    91	1. Employee identifies need for purchase
    92	2. Initiates purchase request through current system (manual or spreadsheet)
    93	3. Requests routed to appropriate supervisor
    94	4. Supervisor reviews and approves (or denies)
    95	5. Once approved, converted to purchase order
    96	6. Information likely re-keyed, creating data entry errors
    97	
    98	**SYSTEMS INVOLVED:** Core (current system), possibly spreadsheets or email
    99	
   100	**PAIN POINTS:**
   101	- Manual re-keying when converting requisitions to POs (error-prone)
   102	- Limited visibility into approval status
   103	- No centralized audit trail for budget compliance
   104	- Time-consuming manual workflow processes
   105	
   106	---
   107	
   108	## 1.3 Orion/NetSuite Solution
   109	
   110	Orion/NetSuite provides comprehensive purchase requisition management that integrates seamlessly with the purchasing process. The proven solution includes automated approval routing based on business rules, supervisor assignment, and one-touch conversion from requisition to purchase order with complete data integrity. Once a supervisor approves a requisition in NetSuite, the system automatically creates the associated purchase order with all information pre-populated—eliminating manual re-keying and the errors that accompany manual data transfer.
   111	
   112	The purchase requisition module in NetSuite includes flexible approval workflows that can route requisitions based on department, cost category, or amount thresholds. Approval histories are automatically recorded and maintained, providing the audit trail necessary for compliance verification and budget accountability. Employees benefit from a clear, transparent process where they can track their submitted requisitions from initial submission through supervisor review to final purchase order generation. Finance teams gain visibility into pending approvals and purchasing activity across the organization.
   113	
   114	This standard functionality is used by thousands of NetSuite customers and represents proven, mature purchasing governance without customization required.
   115	
   116	---
   117	
   118	## 1.4 Future State Process
   119	
   120	**PROCESS:** Purchase Requisition with Automatic Conversion (Future State)
