_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Commissions.md:189:- REQ\-3\.01\.05: Support date\-based validity for commission plans with fiscal year alignment
_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Commissions.md:193:Pivot currently manages multiple compensation plans across different sales roles\. The current commission plans are based on cumulative annual calculations tied to calendar year and invoice date\.
_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Commissions.md:205:- As a Commission Administrator, I need automated cumulative annual commission calculations so that we can eliminate manual tracking and ensure accurate, timely commission payments\.
_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Commissions.md:209:NetSuite Orion's Commission Module will be configured to support Pivot's cumulative annual calculation methodology\. As decided during discovery: "We will build cumulative annual functionality into the Orion module to support the existing commission structure\. Calendar year and based on invoice date\."
