_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Financial_Management.md:1752:Pivot's current AR management in D365 lacks integrated dashboard visibility with project IDs\. The team runs weekly aging reports that require manual augmentation to include certain fields needed for internal questioning and analysis\.
_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Financial_Management.md:1754:As documented in discovery: "Use various dashboards but lack integrated view with all needed information\. Need project ID visibility for internal questioning" – highlighting the need for real\-time AR dashboards with embedded project context\.
_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Financial_Management.md:1765:- As an AR Manager, I need integrated AR dashboards with project visibility so that I can quickly answer internal questions without running and augmenting reports\.
_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Financial_Management.md:1769:NetSuite Orion provides comprehensive AR dashboard capabilities with built\-in project integration and customizable aging reports that eliminate manual augmentation requirements\.
