_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Financial_Management.md:1780:NetSuite Orion's enhanced dashboards provide furniture dealer\-specific project visibility integrated with AR aging, eliminating the need for manual report augmentation\. Dashboards are configurable to display the specific fields and KPIs Pivot needs for internal questioning, eliminating the need to run separate reports for routine inquiries\. Project IDs are integrated throughout AR records, enabling drill\-down from dashboard to transaction to project with full project context\.
