./Financial Management/KBMH/3 Output/BRD_FinancialManagement_v2.0.md:463:Tax exemption certificates are managed within SuiteTax with automatic expiration tracking and dashboard alerts. When certificates approach expiration, the dashboard flags them for renewal, preventing accidental tax charging on exempt transactions. The system maintains a complete audit trail of certificate updates and renewals for compliance reporting.
./Financial Management/KBMH/3 Output/BRD_FinancialManagement_v2.0.md:469:KB+Hoag's finance team will maintain tax compliance through automated SuiteTax processing. Tax rates are automatically determined by NetSuite based on ship-to addresses and transaction types. Tax exemption certificates are uploaded to the system and tracked automatically with dashboard alerts 30 days before expiration. Finance staff review the expiration dashboard monthly to identify certificates requiring renewal. Use tax for IL/MO is calculated automatically without requiring manual workarounds. At month-end, the team runs standard SuiteTax reports organized by ship-to location for state filings and analysis.
