05:24","endTime":"05:27","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So.","startTime":"05:27","endTime":"05:28","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But that's going well.","startTime":"05:29","endTime":"05:30","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I think it takes me back to my early accounting days when like to post things.","startTime":"05:31","endTime":"05:36","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"You had to code things into like an AS400 machine or something, you know, wasn't.","startTime":"05:36","endTime":"05:41","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Yeah, wasn't the easy stuff like we're.","startTime":"05:41","endTime":"05:43","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Going to talk about today.","startTime":"05:43","endTime":"05:44","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"05:44","endTime":"05:45","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"So, okay, so we got a lot of work to do today.","startTime":"05:47","endTime":"05:50","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"05:51","endTime":"05:53","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Don't know how you want us to start or do you want us to share what we've done or.","startTime":"05:53","endTime":"05:58","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Yeah, we'll kind of hit the topics.","startTime":"05:59","endTime":"06:01","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I have just a lot of questions, so we can just talk through some topics.","startTime":"06:02","endTime":"06:06","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"The main goal is to get that all out onto the transcript so that we can absorb it and better put together.","startTime":"06:06","endTime":"06:11","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I think after this session, as long as we get through most of the topics, we will be in a good place to start creating the financial brd.","startTime":"06:11","endTime":"06:21","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"That's really the goal of this.","startTime":"06:21","endTime":"06:22","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Some of the other sections were actually really close on the BRDs because of how much were able to cover in the sessions on site.","startTime":"06:24","endTime":"06:30","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So we will be in good shape.","startTime":"06:31","endTime":"06:33","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We will have in the coming weeks, like we just want to make sure that the BRDs are completely polished.","startTime":"06:34","endTime":"06:39","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Like, that is the kind of the book that we work from when we're implementing the account.","startTime":"06:39","endTime":"06:43","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So I, I don't know if I've talked to you guys about this, maybe just mentioned it in passing, but we take all of this documentation, we review it internally.","startTime":"06:44","endTime":"06:53","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"You know, Gary and Janine are creating drafts of the brd.","startTime":"06:54","endTime":"06:58","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I'm helping with some of that stuff, but we're just trying to, like, we have our original discovery questionnaire, everything that we need to answer in order to create a good brd.","startTime":"06:58","endTime":"07:07","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So we create the BRD as complete as possible.","startTime":"07:07","endTime":"07:10","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We're categorizing things in terms of does it accommodate.","startTime":"07:10","endTime":"07:15","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I'm sorry, I'm using the wrong terminology already.","startTime":"07:15","endTime":"07:17","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Does it align with exactly how you guys are doing it and there's no change for either party.","startTime":"07:18","endTime":"07:24","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Do you guys need to adapt to how Orion does it, or do you guys have something special in your process that's making you win that we want to accommodate.","startTime":"07:25","endTime":"07:34","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Anything that ends up in that accommodate section on these BRDs warrants further conversation.","startTime":"07:35","endTime":"07:41","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So it could be anything.","startTime":"07:42","endTime":"07:44","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"It could be as small as, like, okay, we have to create a small saved search or a report that's pretty easy, low level.","startTime":"07:44","endTime":"07:50","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Like, it's not going to really affect the BRD or the statement of work at all.","startTime":"07:50","endTime":"07:54","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"It might be a script that adds a couple hours to the project, or it might be that we need to make a module specific for you guys.","startTime":"07:55","endTime":"08:02","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"If a module is made specific for you guys, it kind of falls into one of two buckets.","startTime":"08:03","endTime":"08:08","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"It's good for the entire dealer network and it gets added to the software either now or at some release in the future or, hey, this is really our special sauce.","startTime":"08:08","endTime":"08:19","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We are willing to pay for this module, but we don't want the rest of the dealer network to have it.","startTime":"08:20","endTime":"08:25","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So that's kind of the big module stuff.","startTime":"08:26","endTime":"08:28","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So it's like if you need it and it will benefit the network, the dealer network, then we build that into the software and it's no cost to anybody that just comes out in a future release.","startTime":"08:28","endTime":"08:41","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But we do have the benefit of working with somebody like you guys to kind of put together the requirements for that module and talk through it in that process.","startTime":"08:41","endTime":"08:50","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I'm sorry, remind me again what BRD stands for?","startTime":"08:51","endTime":"08:54","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Business Requirements Document.","startTime":"08:54","endTime":"08:56","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So basically what we're saying in that document is, hey, here's what we understand from going through the discovery process.","startTime":"08:57","endTime":"09:05","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Okay, Here is the current state, here is your business requirement, and this is how we approach each one of those business requirements.","startTime":"09:06","endTime":"09:15","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So like I said, each requirement is going to fall into one of those three buckets.","startTime":"09:16","endTime":"09:20","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Align, adapt, or accommodate.","startTime":"09:21","endTime":"09:23","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And we spell that all out right in the BRD.","startTime":"09:23","endTime":"09:26","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So then we hand these BRDs over to you guys and you review them.","startTime":"09:26","endTime":"09:30","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And that's a bit of a process, right, like you're going through making comments on it.","startTime":"09:30","endTime":"09:34","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I don't quite understand what you're talking about here.","startTime":"09:34","endTime":"09:36","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Can I have a little bit more clarification?","startTime":"09:36","endTime":"09:38","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Ideally it doesn't come down to like, no, you guys didn't get this, like, let's rewrite it.","startTime":"09:39","endTime":"09:43","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But then we give you the BRDs, we walk through the commenting process and then we reconcile all those comments and then we issue a finalized BRD that you guys sign off on as this is specifically what we're going to do for this process area.","startTime":"09:43","endTime":"09:57","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So normally we publish eight business requirement documents.","startTime":"09:57","endTime":"10:05","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So that's everything like pre quo order management, financial business intelligence, etc.","startTime":"10:05","endTime":"10:11","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So we.","startTime":"10:11","endTime":"10:12","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"That's what we're in the process.","startTime":"10:12","endTime":"10:13","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I have three that I think are like 95% ready for.","startTime":"10:13","endTime":"10:18","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"For BRDs to be created.","startTime":"10:20","endTime":"10:22","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"There might need to be some just back and forth over email to answer a few remaining questions.","startTime":"10:22","endTime":"10:26","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And then the big financial management operations, that's going to be a little lighter for you guys.","startTime":"10:26","endTime":"10:32","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And then order management are the big ones that usually take the longest to produce and the longest for the commenting process.","startTime":"10:32","endTime":"10:38","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So I'd really like to wrap up.","startTime":"10:39","endTime":"10:41","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I don't.","startTime":"10:42","endTime":"10:43","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"10:43","endTime":"10:43","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"If we can get through most of these things, I'm going to rerun, like my business questionnaire, completeness assessment, and then we may be in a good spot to issue that BRD after that.","startTime":"10:43","endTime":"10:53","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Okay, so the one thing that we've talked about quite a bit and I'm just gonna, I'll launch right into it.","startTime":"10:54","endTime":"10:59","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Unless you have anything specific, Debbie.","startTime":"10:59","endTime":"11:01","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"No, we've got the outline.","startTime":"11:01","endTime":"11:03","speaker_name":"Debbie Herbert","speaker_id":4},{"sentence":"Fire away.","startTime":"11:03","endTime":"11:03","speaker_name":"Debbie Herbert","speaker_id":4},{"sentence":"Yep.","startTime":"11:03","endTime":"11:04","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Okay, so the chart of accounts, you guys have this 40 page chart of accounts.","startTime":"11:04","endTime":"11:09","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We gave you our chart of accounts.","startTime":"11:10","endTime":"11:12","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I've built a little tool that will take an Excel sheet, compare it to our chart of accounts and make some suggestions.","startTime":"11:12","endTime":"11:21","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We actually already did that.","startTime":"11:22","endTime":"11:23","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"So that's.","startTime":"11:23","endTime":"11:23","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"We already did that.","startTime":"11:24","endTime":"11:25","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"So if you want to jump into.","startTime":"11:25","endTime":"11:27","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"It, I'll have Kevin bring it up so you can all look at it.","startTime":"11:27","endTime":"11:30","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"That would be amazing.","startTime":"11:30","endTime":"11:30","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"If we could just go through what you guys found.","startTime":"11:30","endTime":"11:32","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"11:32","endTime":"11:33","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"11:33","endTime":"11:34","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"All right, let me show.","startTime":"11:34","endTime":"11:35","speaker_name":"Kevin Yin","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Make it bigger, please.","startTime":"11:39","endTime":"11:40","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Okay, so just to show you here, everything in row B, column B, C, D and E. Is what came from you guys.","startTime":"11:46","endTime":"11:56","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Yes.","startTime":"11:56","endTime":"11:56","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So those are the Orion numbers, obviously.","startTime":"11:56","endTime":"11:59","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Sorry, F. The Orion kind of titles, if you will, stuff.","startTime":"11:59","endTime":"12:02","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Yep.","startTime":"12:02","endTime":"12:03","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"What we did then in column G, H, I, J and K is like.","startTime":"12:04","endTime":"12:09","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"We matched up our current core accounts.","startTime":"12:09","endTime":"12:13","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"And tried to map them to your account.","startTime":"12:13","endTime":"12:16","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"12:16","endTime":"12:16","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"We've highlighted what are new, the things that we need.","startTime":"12:16","endTime":"12:20","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"And then in column H is the important one because that's active or closed.","startTime":"12:20","endTime":"12:25","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"However, if it's closed and we still need it's because there's history in it.","startTime":"12:26","endTime":"12:30","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"And that's the, that's our problem.","startTime":"12:30","endTime":"12:32","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"That although we'd love to go cleaner and smoother and, you know, more condensed, we still have history in a bunch of crappy camps, so.","startTime":"12:32","endTime":"12:43","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"And since we've committed to bringing in the seven years of history, we're unfortunately.","startTime":"12:43","endTime":"12:48","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Going to need these accounts.","startTime":"12:48","endTime":"12:49","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"So.","startTime":"12:50","endTime":"12:50","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"So that's kind of what we've done here.","startTime":"12:51","endTime":"12:53","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"So with that overlay, I don't know.","startTime":"12:53","endTime":"12:56","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"If you want to go row by row or how.","startTime":"12:56","endTime":"12:59","speaker_name":"Lorraine Guzman","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Yeah, we can kind of.","startTime":"12:59","endTime":"13:00","speaker_name":"Kevin Yin","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"I think we can kind of talk in big chunks here.","startTime":"13:00","endTime":"13:03","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Like, you've kind of laid out a lot of the big chunks.","startTime":"13:03","endTime":"13:06","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So let's talk about history for a minute.","startTime":"13:06","endTime":"13:09","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We're going to bring in all of the, all of this history.","startTime":"13:09","endTime":"13:12","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I don't know if we've decided on an exact data migration strategy, but for the ones that are kind of historical only will, like, you won't be writing data to them in Orion.","startTime":"13:12","endTime":"13:25","speaker_name":"Chris Trumb