ua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Having a labor quote dashboard so you can see everything that's been quoted.","startTime":"20:01","endTime":"20:04","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"To be able to see who's with what and what status they are at and what's getting sent out to whom would be helpful.","startTime":"20:06","endTime":"20:13","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"20:13","endTime":"20:14","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"We look at right now who we're doing labor with.","startTime":"20:14","endTime":"20:17","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"It would be nice to see who's quoting and we could see how often quote versus actual what we're awarding.","startTime":"20:17","endTime":"20:24","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Gotcha.","startTime":"20:25","endTime":"20:26","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Yep.","startTime":"20:26","endTime":"20:27","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"That's across all projects.","startTime":"20:27","endTime":"20:29","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"20:29","endTime":"20:30","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Yes.","startTime":"20:30","endTime":"20:31","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Across all projects.","startTime":"20:31","endTime":"20:32","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"20:32","endTime":"20:32","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We could put on that dashboard.","startTime":"20:32","endTime":"20:33","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We'll put.","startTime":"20:33","endTime":"20:34","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We'll put some filters on there.","startTime":"20:34","endTime":"20:35","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So you could filter it to a specific location or a specific division or even a specific order team member that way.","startTime":"20:36","endTime":"20:44","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Otherwise you'll be looking at a lot.","startTime":"20:45","endTime":"20:46","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"20:47","endTime":"20:47","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Which will be another reason too, at some point to maybe have an official rejection process.","startTime":"20:48","endTime":"20:55","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Because if something does get officially rejected, it comes off the dashboard.","startTime":"20:55","endTime":"20:59","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So another thing to consider.","startTime":"20:59","endTime":"21:00","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But you could.","startTime":"21:00","endTime":"21:01","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"That could even be like an end of the month cleanup.","startTime":"21:01","endTime":"21:03","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Well, I guess my question is if, like we.","startTime":"21:04","endTime":"21:06","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"If there's three labor quotes.","startTime":"21:06","endTime":"21:07","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Well, this is where I guess it could get confusing and we could dive in this deeper.","startTime":"21:08","endTime":"21:11","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"But something to just think about is.","startTime":"21:11","endTime":"21:12","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Like, okay, we initially went out, got.","startTime":"21:12","endTime":"21:16","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Three labor quotes for a project, we accept one, but then we have to go out and get labor quotes again because their scope change.","startTime":"21:16","endTime":"21:24","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So we might have to accept another one.","startTime":"21:25","endTime":"21:28","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So there might be more than one labor quote on A project.","startTime":"21:30","endTime":"21:33","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"It's one thing to think about.","startTime":"21:33","endTime":"21:34","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Ideally, though, if you like, I sent out three and I picked one.","startTime":"21:35","endTime":"21:40","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"The other two would just be rejected.","startTime":"21:40","endTime":"21:41","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"It would close those out because I picked one.","startTime":"21:42","endTime":"21:44","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"But I don't know how they're tied together or if they are tied together in any way.","startTime":"21:44","endTime":"21:47","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So.","startTime":"21:48","endTime":"21:48","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah, there might be a way.","startTime":"21:50","endTime":"21:51","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"There might be a way that we could.","startTime":"21:51","endTime":"21:53","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We could think through that.","startTime":"21:53","endTime":"21:54","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So an action item for us is to think through the potential automatic rejection of subsequent labor quotes.","startTime":"21:54","endTime":"22:01","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speak