4:13","endTime":"24:14","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Are you doing any of your own internal estimating at all?","startTime":"24:14","endTime":"24:16","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Well, only on design npm.","startTime":"24:17","endTime":"24:20","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"24:20","endTime":"24:21","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"24:21","endTime":"24:21","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"24:21","endTime":"24:22","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Not on the install.","startTime":"24:22","endTime":"24:23","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"24:23","endTime":"24:23","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Not on the install.","startTime":"24:23","endTime":"24:24","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Okay, very good.","startTime":"24:25","endTime":"24:26","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"If you mean that when we forget to get a label quote for something small and we go, I think that's $300, and then we hope we're right about it.","startTime":"24:28","endTime":"24:35","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah, that happens a lot actually, Marcus.","startTime":"24:35","endTime":"24:37","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"I know.","startTime":"24:38","endTime":"24:38","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I was gonna say, how much do.","startTime":"24:38","endTime":"24:40","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"You think it would cost to do this?","startTime":"24:40","endTime":"24:43","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah, yeah, no, I'm typically asking that question to see if you have any expec