ts, but not always.","startTime":"49:09","endTime":"49:11","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah, got it now.","startTime":"49:12","endTime":"49:15","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"So that's that.","startTime":"49:15","endTime":"49:16","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So that's how Orion works.","startTime":"49:16","endTime":"49:17","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Right.","startTime":"49:17","endTime":"49:17","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Now, if we wanted to do something around the account manager where, like, if the account manager gets assigned to a opportunity, in this case, then These other people are automatically assigned.","startTime":"49:17","endTime":"49:29","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We don't currently have that now.","startTime":"49:29","endTime":"49:31","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Now it.","startTime":"49:31","endTime":"49:32","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"You can say, all right, let me sign this account manager.","startTime":"49:32","endTime":"49:35","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And I know that these other people go with this account manager.","startTime":"49:35","endTime":"49:37","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I can just manually assign them.","startTime":"49:37","endTime":"49:38","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I just wanted.","startTime":"49:39","endTime":"49:40","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So if that's okay, then you have the ability to do that.","startTime":"49:40","endTime":"49:43","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Yeah, that's fine.","startTime":"49:43","endTime":"49:44","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"That's what we do today.","startTime":"49:44","endTime":"49:44","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"49:45","endTime":"49:45","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"49:46","endTime":"49:46","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Right.","startTime":"49:47","endTime":"49:47","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Kimi?","startTime":"49:47","endTime":"49:48","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"49:49","endTime":"49:50","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"If there's an associated.","startTime":"49:50","endTime":"49:51","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"And there was typically be always the same PC and then maybe pm, maybe designer.","startTime":"49:51","endTime":"49:58","speaker_name":"Kimi Katsuyoshi","speaker_id":3},{"sentence":"Yeah, exactly.","startTime":"49:58","endTime":"49:59","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"But the PC is usually the one doing it.","startTime":"49:59","endTime":"50:01","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So they usually assign themselves and then they start flowing it.","startTime":"50:01","endTime":"50:05","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah, okay, got it.","startTime":"50:05","endTime":"50:07","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"And then.","startTime":"50:09","endTime":"50:09","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I'm sorry, did I already ask about pm?","startTime":"50:09","endTime":"50:11","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"The request for pm.","startTime":"50:12","endTime":"50:13","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So the request for pm.","startTime":"50:13","endTime":"50:15","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Yes.","startTime":"50:15","endTime":"50:15","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"We don't have a formal request for pm.","startTime":"50:16","endTime":"50:18","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"It's team based.","startTime":"50:18","endTime":"50:20","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"50:21","endTime":"50:21","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"So use.","startTime":"50:21","endTime":"50:22","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"Yeah, there's a PM that's not available.","startTime":"50:22","endTime":"50:24","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"Then they usually come to me to find another pm.","startTime":"50:24","endTime":"50:27","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"Right, I'm sorry.","startTime":"50:27","endTime":"50:28","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Or they'll find somebody themselves.","startTime":"50:29","endTime":"50:31","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"What's the timing on that?","startTime":"50:31","endTime":"50:32","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"At what point does the PM get involved?","startTime":"50:32","endTime":"50:34","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We're all laughing, right?","startTime":"50:38","endTime":"50:39","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"Sometimes we get a year in advance and sometimes we get an hour in advance.","startTime":"50:41","endTime":"50:44","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"It just depends on who's requesting and what they've been given.","startTime":"50:44","endTime":"50:48","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So in advance of what?","startTime":"50:48","endTime":"50:50","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"This scheduling.","startTime":"50:50","endTime":"50:52","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Great question, Markus.","startTime":"50:52","endTime":"50:54","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"50:55","endTime":"50:55","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"My experience has been, I mean obviously the PMs want to have dates for visibility so they can see how their workflow is and if they're available to PM a project.","startTime":"50:57","endTime":"51:06","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"But there's times where dates slip and.","startTime":"51:07","endTime":"51:09","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"And so that means they'll have a conflict and that's when something.","startTime":"51:11","endTime":"51:16","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"That's when something may change.","startTime":"51:16","endTime":"51:18","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"So yeah, it's.","startTime":"51:18","endTime":"51:19","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"We try to get signed as early as possible.","startTime":"51:19","endTime":"51:21","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"51:22","endTime":"51:22","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"And then because there's more than just the install that we have to do.","startTime":"51:22","endTime":"51:25","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Right.","startTime":"51:25","endTime":"51:26","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"There's a lot of pre work that has to happen.","startTime":"51:26","endTime":"51:28","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So we don't always get that or our client doesn't always provide the AM the opportunity to do that.","startTime":"51:28","endTime":"51:34","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"But that's what we're seeking.","startTime":"51:34","endTime":"51:35","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Is this because we would like to assign a PM at the opportunity level?","startTime":"51:35","endTime":"51:39","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Not at the order level.","startTime":"51:39","endTime":"51:41","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"But right now it's usually happening at the order level.","startTime":"51:41","endTime":"51:43","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Got it.","startTime":"51:44","endTime":"51:45","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Would you like a reminder on somebody's dashboard that says here are orders booked without a pm.","startTime":"51:46","endTime":"51:53","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Would that be helpful?","startTime":"51:55","endTime":"51:56","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"51:57","endTime":"51:57","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Not just PM too.","startTime":"51:57","endTime":"51:59","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"It's sometimes because I run bookings reports and what I notice missing a lot is account managers, somebody.","startTime":"51:59","endTime":"52:04","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"It's usually not big orders but regardless, every order should have an account.","startTime":"52:04","endTime":"52:08","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"So yeah, a reminder of some kind that would say, hey, this is missing a PC.","startTime":"52:09","endTime":"52:12","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"This is missing a.","startTime":"52:12","endTime":"52:14","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"All of my orders would just be showing up on your dashboard code.","startTime":"52:16","endTime":"52:18","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"You can keep looking at them if you want to.","startTime":"52:18","endTime":"52:20","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Yeah, those are some pretty simple things for us to do.","startTime":"52:22","endTime":"52:25","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Netsuite has a very useful tool called Save Searches.","startTime":"52:25","endTime":"52:29","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"It's just a way to query.","startTime":"52:30","endTime":"52:31","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Write a query and then you can make a reminder out of it on your dashboard.","startTime":"52:31","endTime":"52:34","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"The other thing we have is this concept of default roles, and we call it default roles, but it's more like a required role.","startTime":"52:35","endTime":"52:42","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And we could say in the system for you specifically that an account manager is a required role.","startTime":"52:43","endTime":"52:49","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And then what happens is on top of the opportunity or the quote or the order, it has a notification center at the top and it'll say account manager is a required role.","startTime":"52:49","endTime":"53:01","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And it's not assigned yet some kind of messaging like that.","startTime":"53:01","endTime":"53:04","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So every time somebody pulls that up, they're reminded of it.","startTime":"53:04","endTime":"53:06","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"It's not like in.","startTime":"53:06","endTime":"53:07","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"There's no sirens, it's not flashing or anything like that.","startTime":"53:08","endTime":"53:10","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"It's.","startTime":"53:10","endTime":"53:10","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"It's there, but it's not obscene.","startTime":"53:11","endTime":"53:12","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But I mean, there are a lot.","startTime":"53:13","endTime":"53:14","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Of orders we process though, without an account manager.","startTime":"53:14","endTime":"53:17","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So, like, I could see that to be annoying.","startTime":"53:17","endTime":"53:19","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"If there are.","startTime":"53:22","endTime":"53:23","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"If there is like some logic.","startTime":"53:23","endTime":"53:25","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I mean, I was thinking of like every single work from home order.","startTime":"53:25","endTime":"53:27","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"There's no account manager on work from home.","startTime":"53:27","endTime":"53:29","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"And I don't think.","startTime":"53:32","endTime":"53:32","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"What about.","startTime":"53:32","endTime":"53:33","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I don't think the intermarket.","startTime":"53:33","endTime":"53:34","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":8},{"sentence":"Intermarket.","startTime":"53:35","endTime":"53:36","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Half the time there's no account manager on an intermarket deal and we're just doing labor only.","startTime":"53:36","endTime":"53:39","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_i