ning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"And I'm just nervous that we're going to lose access to the SQL when they cut off Desktop.","startTime":"59:23","endTime":"59:29","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"We need to be thinking about that data transfer and when we're going to do it and when we're going to start it and what it's going to look like.","startTime":"59:30","endTime":"59:37","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"And maybe we want to do an initial upfront just to grab what we have to date in case we do lose access for some reason.","startTime":"59:37","endTime":"59:44","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So, Matt, I talked to them about that when I was there at Corcon, and I mean, this is Joe the developer speaking.","startTime":"59:45","endTime":"59:52","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"It wasn't John the owner.","startTime":"59:52","endTime":"59:53","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"So you have to take it with a grain of salt.","startTime":"59:53","endTime":"59:55","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"But I obviously didn't tell him why I was concerned.","startTime":"59:55","endTime":"59:58","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"I Said, yeah, I know we can't write to the old databases, but we GSI query those quite often and we pull data and we need run reports and things.","startTime":"59:58","endTime":"01:00:05","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"And he said, you will not lose access to the MySQL and you won't lose access to desktop.","startTime":"01:00:05","endTime":"01:00:11","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"He said, it's view only access, but that's.","startTime":"01:00:11","endTime":"01:00:15","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"I mean, that's all.","startTime":"01:00:15","endTime":"01:00:16","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"That's all we need.","startTime":"01:00:16","endTime":"01:00:17","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"We only have view only access in the back end now anyway.","startTime":"01:00:17","endTime":"01:00:20","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"So again, take it with a grain of salt, but he assured me that we're not going to lose access, so we'll see.","startTime":"01:00:20","endTime":"01:00:25","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"All right, well, you know me, I'm.","startTime":"01:00:25","endTime":"01:00:28","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"A doomsday prepper, so let's run around it in case something happens.","startTime":"01:00:28","endTime":"01:00:33","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"So.","startTime":"01:00:33","endTime":"01:00:33","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"No, I had the exact same thought.","startTime":"01:00:33","endTime":"01:00:35","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"That's why I asked him.","startTime":"01:00:35","endTime":"01:00:36","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"I was panicked.","startTime":"01:00:36","endTime":"01:00:37","speaker_name":"Kip Herdrick","speaker_id":7},{"sentence":"So let's.","startTime":"01:00:37","endTime":"01:00:38","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So it's not too early to start this.","startTime":"01:00:38","endTime":"01:00:40","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So, Kip, I'm going to start a conversation.","startTime":"01:00:40","endTime":"01:00:42","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I think I can do this on teams.","startTime":"01:00:42","endTime":"01:00:44","speaker_name":"Marcus Dallacqua","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I'm going to start a conversation with you and our team member Joe, and he's the one who handles all the