./Order Management/KBMH/2 Input/Master_Transcript_Order_Management.md:15:Order Management at KBM Hoag encompasses the entire transaction lifecycle from quote/proposal creation through sales order booking, purchase order generation, and invoicing. The current Core system treats proposals and sales orders as a single transaction with status changes, while NetSuite/Orion uses separate, linked transactions. Key challenges include Miller Knoll tiered pricing complexities, tax management for government/direct bill orders, customer PO tracking, approval workflows, and managing split orders for installation strategies. The team emphasizes they operate in a "collapsed" world where all work is done upfront before creating a static proposal.
