","endTime":"10:35","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"So I. I think that there has to be a warehouse in the system.","startTime":"10:36","endTime":"10:40","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Well, okay.","startTime":"10:41","endTime":"10:42","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Because yeah, even now we still receive and we received to have been encore, but we just.","startTime":"10:42","endTime":"10:48","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Well, we received to a location encore warehouse location, which we just put as zero.","startTime":"10:48","endTime":"10:54","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But.","startTime":"10:56","endTime":"10:56","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But it doesn't require them to be set up.","startTime":"10:56","endTime":"10:58","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Well, I guess maybe here I'm just going to send you everything.","startTime":"10:59","endTime":"11:03","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Then when we do the next demo, you can remind me how that attaches at the order level.","startTime":"11:04","endTime":"11:09","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Sure.","startTime":"11:10","endTime":"11:10","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Because this could be like a no big deal thing that I'm making a big deal right now.","startTime":"11:12","endTime":"11:15","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So let's just say I'm going to send you the whole list and then we'll talk about it at the next demo.","startTime":"11:15","endTime":"11:20","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"All right, sounds great.","startTime":"11:21","endTime":"11:22","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"And then for those warehouses, you know, it sounds like in core they don't 