artTime":"13:20","endTime":"13:23","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"The netsuite native version.","startTime":"13:23","endTime":"13:25","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"It's just literally drag and drop.","startTime":"13:25","endTime":"13:27","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"You can select everything, drag it into one bin.","startTime":"13:27","endTime":"13:29","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"It's.","startTime":"13:29","endTime":"13:29","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"It does all of the documentation in the background, creates item receipts.","startTime":"13:29","endTime":"13:34","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"It's all pretty.","startTime":"13:34","endTime":"13:34","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Pretty smooth there.","startTime":"13:34","endTime":"13:35","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Okay, cool.","startTime":"13:36","endTime":"13:37","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Okay, so in the future.","startTime":"13:39","endTime":"13:41","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"No.","startTime":"13:41","endTime":"13:41","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"No contractors will probably need direct receiving capability.","startTime":"13:42","endTime":"13:45","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"It's something on our wish list, but not anything we're focused on at the moment.","startTime":"13:47","endTime":"13:50","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Okay, that's good.","startTime":"13:51","endTime":"13:53","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"So we have the vendor, like, the vendor portal, which includes, like subcontractors.","startTime":"13:55","endTime":"14:02","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"It's kind of in.","startTime":"14:02","endTime":"14:03","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"It's in progress right now.","startTime":"14:03","endTime":"14:05","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"So we want to ask a few questions as we're finalizing that to make sure that we're either covering exactly what you need now or that we are keeping kind of the future state in mind.","startTime":"14:05","endTime":"14:16","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"So when you have subcontractors, what are they logging into right now?","startTime":"14:18","endTime":"14:24","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"What do they have access to see?","startTime":"14:24","endTime":"14:26","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"What does that interaction look like?","startTime":"14:26","endTime":"14:28","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"They have nothing.","startTime":"14:29","endTime":"14:29","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"They have nothing.","startTime":"14:30","endTime":"14:31","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":0},{"sentence":"Okay, yeah, we send them PDFs of all the receivers so they know what's coming.","startTime":"14:31","endTime":"14:35","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"We send them a PDF of their po.","startTime":"14:35","endTime":"14:37","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Okay.","startTime":"14:38","endTime":"14:38","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So I mean the most automation we have at this point is CORE sends them that information automatically when we cut their po.","startTime":"14:39","endTime":"14:49","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But that's about it.","startTime":"14:49","endTime":"14:50","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I have done a few projects matches where service left has access to the actual status report, which is a Google sheet outside of Core.","startTime":"14:51","endTime":"14:59","speaker_name":"+14*******45","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"So they.","startTime":"14:59","endTime":"15:00","speaker_name":"+14*******45","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"They see a box link to or drive link to the actual receivers that they've already given us for a given project.","startTime":"15:02","endTime":"15:10","speaker_name":"+14*******45","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"So all the information is in one place.","startTime":"15:10","endTime":"15:13","speaker_name":"+14*******45","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"Yeah.","startTime":"15:14","endTime":"15:14","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"So yeah, I was going to say right now nothing out of the system is shared, but we share a lot of files through DRIVE.","startTime":"15:14","endTime":"15:20","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"For our primary partners that we work with.","startTime":"15:22","endTime":"15:25","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"I would like them to be able to access information in Orion directly through the vendor portal and that would be POS that have been issued to them.","startTime":"15:25","endTime":"15:34","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Receivers for projects.","startTime":"15:34","endTime":"15:36","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"And schedule and status reports.","startTime":"15:38","endTime":"15:41","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Projects, product status reports.","startTime":"15:41","endTime":"15:43","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"Is there a need to have kind of like a notify of arrival of products or anything like that?","startTime":"15:44","endTime":"15:49","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Well, I mean they're going to be notifying us of arrival, so yeah, that's what 