?","startTime":"41:36","endTime":"41:43","speaker_name":"+14*******45","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"Like are there different information?","startTime":"41:43","endTime":"41:44","speaker_name":"+14*******45","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"Yeah, it can have different information.","startTime":"41:45","endTime":"41:47","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"It can have different fields and then it drives.","startTime":"41:47","endTime":"41:50","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"You can drive different things like reporting on work order types.","startTime":"41:50","endTime":"41:53","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"You can get into time tracking by order type.","startTime":"41:53","endTime":"41:56","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"You can do permissions by type.","startTime":"41:56","endTime":"41:59","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"There's all different things that you can.","startTime":"41:59","endTime":"42:02","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"And there's also like kind of a skills matrix of what resources can be assigned to these different work order types as well.","startTime":"42:02","endTime":"42:09","speaker_name":"Chris Trumble","speaker_id":1},{"sentence":"Well, this definitely is outside of my sandbox, but it feels like overcomplicated.","startTime":"42:10","endTime":"42:14","speaker_name":"+14*******45","speaker_id":6},{"sentence":"It does, but for.","startTime":"42:16","endTime":"42:17","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"I like it for a tracking standpoint, honestly.","startTime":"42:17","endTime":"42:20","speaker_name":"Matt Denning","speaker_id":2},{"sentence":"But like for like let's say an account manager, they needed a site verification.","startTime":"42:21","endTime":"42:26","speaker_name":"Wendy Stark","speaker_id":5},{"sentence":"Would they.","startTime":"42:27","endTime":"42:27